den Society Newsletter''\n | url=http://audensociety.org/archives.html\n | accessdate = 21 January 2007\n}}\n-->\n*{{cite web\n | title=The W. H. Auden Society\n | url=http://audensociety.org/ \n | accessdate = 21 January 2007\n}}\n*{{cite web\n | title=Fourteen poems by Auden (Academy of American Poets site)\n | url=http://www.poets.org/poet.php/prmPID/120 \n | accessdate = 20 January 2007\n}}\n*{{cite web\n | title=W. H. Auden at Swarthmore\n | url=http://www.swarthmore.edu/library/auden \n | accessdate = 20 January 2007\n}}\n<!--\n*{{cite web\n | title=Kindred Britain (extensive genealogical website originally focused on Auden)\n | url=http://www.stanford.edu/group/auden/cgi-bin/auden\n | accessdate = 18 November 2012\n}}\n-->\n* [https://www.bl.uk/people/w-h-auden ''W H Auden''] at the British Library\n*[http://pid.emory.edu/ark:/25593/8xxxn Papers] at [https://rose.library.emory.edu/ Stuart A. Rose Manuscript, Archives, and Rare Book Library]\n<!--\n* [http://lib.slu.edu/about/associates/literary-award 1970 Recipient of the St. Louis Literary Award]\n-->\n\n{{W. H. Auden}}\n{{Navboxes|list=\n{{PulitzerPrize PoetryAuthors 1922\u20131950}}\n{{Austrian State Prize for European Literature}}\n{{svplaureats}}\n}}\n{{subject bar |portal1=Biography |portal2=Poetry |commons=yes |commons-search=Category:W.H. Auden |q=yes |s=yes |s-search=Author:Wystan Hugh Auden |d=yes |d-search=Q178698}}\n{{Authority control}}\n{{good article}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Auden, W. H.}}\n[[Category:1907 births]]\n[[Category:1973 deaths]]\n[[Category:Alumni of Christ Church, Oxford]]\n[[Category:Anglican poets]]\n[[Category:Anthologists]]\n[[Category:British people of the Spanish Civil War]]\n[[Category:English dramatists and playwrights]]\n[[Category:English emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:English literary critics]]\n[[Category:Formalist poets]]\n[[Category:Gay writers]]\n[[Category:Guggenheim Fellows]]\n[[Category:LGBT writers from England]]\n[[Category:Members of the American Academ